Class JDOMXPath

  • java.lang.Object

    Deprecated. 
    replaced by compiled version.

    @Deprecated
public class JDOMXPath
extends XPath
    A concrete XPath implementation for Jaxen. This class must be public because the main JDOM XPath class needs to access the class, and the constructor. The generic type of the returned values from this XPath instance.
